      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p>@Icon[type:graviton] Graviton Revelation</p>\n<p>When you use the gravity surge revelation, you can choose to attempt a bull rush combat maneuver instead of a disarm or trip combat maneuver. You can attempt this bull rush from any direction, regardless of your position relative to the target.</p>\n<div>\n<p>When you’re attuned or fully attuned, if you bull rush a creature using gravity surge and that creature’s movement would be checked by another creature of its size or smaller or by an obstacle, you attempt a trip combat maneuver against each creature as if using the gravity surge revelation. You must have the gravity surge revelation to select this revelation.</p>\n</div>"
